      "message": "These if blocks can be folded into the `for` as\n```\nfor feature in features + [variant.arch_variant, variant.cpu_variant]:\n  if feature:\n    ret.append(\"//build/bazel/platforms/arch/variants:\" + feature)\n```\nwhich itself can be\n`[\"//build/bazel/platforms/arch/variants:\" + feat for feature in features + [variant.arch_variant, variant.cpu_variant] if feat]`\n\nIn case you find either is more readable and/or maintanable.",
